About Us — Expert Custom Crating Solutions in Las Vegas

Welcome to Crates of Las Vegas, your trusted provider of premium custom crating solutions in Las Vegas with reliable nationwide shipping support. With years of hands-on experience designing and building custom wood crates, we specialize in delivering durable, secure packaging that protects valuable items during transport and storage—no matter the size or complexity.
Premium Custom Crates Built for Protection & Peace of Mind

At Crates of Las Vegas, we understand that no two shipments are the same. That’s why we design and build custom wooden crates in Las Vegas using high-quality materials and proven construction methods to ensure maximum protection. Whether you’re shipping fragile artwork, heavy machinery, antiques, or oversized equipment, our tailored crating solutions are built to:

Protect items from damage and impact

Withstand demanding transit conditions

Support safe storage, handling, and transportation

We also offer flexible shipping options across the United States, from local Las Vegas deliveries to coast-to-coast transport.

Your One-Stop Partner for Crating, Packaging & Shipping

Our experienced team manages every stage of the process—from initial consultation and custom design to fabrication and logistics coordination. Whether you need on-site crating services, custom wood crates, or shipping containers, we provide solutions designed around your exact requirements, timeline, and budget.

Our core services include:

Custom Crate Design & Fabrication tailored to weight, dimensions, and fragility

Premium Shipping Containers for long-distance and international transport

Full Packing & Crating Services, including cushioning, wrapping, and secure sealing

Logistics & Transportation Support with nationwide delivery options

